      <title>南非调整通胀目标以保持价格稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/south-africa-inflation-target-review-to-preserve-price-stability</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非财政部副部长戴维·马松多 (David Masondo) 表示，南非央行目前正在对 3% 至 6% 的通胀目标进行审查，并将以保持价格稳定的原则为基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/south-africa-inflation-target-review-to-preserve-price-stability</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
