    <item>
      <title>巴西石油公司准备重振使巴西成为石油巨头的油田</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/petrobras-s-tupi-field-that-made-brazil-a-key-oil-exporter-poised-for-overhaul</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西国有石油公司即将与政府监管机构达成协议，允许其继续推进重新开发大型深水油田的计划，此举可能重振巴西停滞的石油产量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/petrobras-s-tupi-field-that-made-brazil-a-key-oil-exporter-poised-for-overhaul</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Steinhoff 前财务主管的审判被推迟至 2025 年初</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/trial-of-steinhoff-s-former-treasury-head-delayed-to-early-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于当地政府正在努力应对七年前导致这家全球零售商濒临破产的会计丑闻的后果，南非法院将针对 Steinhoff International Holdings NV 前财务主管的案件推迟至 2 月 14 日审理。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/trial-of-steinhoff-s-former-treasury-head-delayed-to-early-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 12:57:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业数据对债券市场造成冲击，交易员撤出对美联储大幅降息的押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/traders-wipe-out-bets-on-big-fed-cuts-as-jobs-data-hits-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国九月份就业数据超出预期并预示着强劲的招聘趋势后，交易员大幅削减了对美联储未来降息步伐的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/traders-wipe-out-bets-on-big-fed-cuts-as-jobs-data-hits-bonds</guid>
