    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布雷纳德称消费者不会感受到港口罢工的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-04/consumers-won-t-feel-impact-of-ports-strike-brainard-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国家经济委员会主任莱尔·布雷纳德 (Lael Brainard) 表示，消费者不会感受到为期三天的美国港口罢工的影响，并表示各方都希望恢复工作。她正在接受“彭博监测”采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-04/consumers-won-t-feel-impact-of-ports-strike-brainard-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 12:46:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德法意敦促欧盟放松银行监管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/germany-france-and-italy-urge-the-eu-to-ease-banking-regulation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国、法国和意大利敦促欧盟在制定金融规则时保持克制，转而将重点放在提高银行业的竞争力上，这是全球政治转向优先考虑经济增长而不是监管的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/germany-france-and-italy-urge-the-eu-to-ease-banking-regulation</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 11:23:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
